        <p>
            <alert>Due Date:</alert> This assignment is due at the beginning of class on Monday, July 6.
        </p>
    </introduction>

    <subsection xml:id="hw2-practice">
        <title>Practice Problems</title>
            <p>
                It is strongly recommended that you complete the below practice problems from the course textbook before beginning the assignment. These solutions do not need to be submitted and will not be graded.
